data.description: Spacious 5 bedrooms and 4 full bathrooms Home On Level Lot just shy of an acre, and backs up to a Scenic Pond that is Fully Stocked with Fish!!! First Level has Hardwood flooring, the Eat-In kitchen Has Breakfast Bar and Breakfast Area, with Modern Stainless Steel Appliances; Large Family Room with Fireplace, Separate Living Room and Dining Room and 5th Bedroom on the Main can be an office; The Huge Master Suite with Sitting Room Features En-suite Master Bathroom with Separate Shower and Soaking Tub and His and Hers Closets! Huge private, level backyard backs up the fully Stocked with Fish Pond, and has a She Shed/Man Cave providing a Private Retreat. This home has a Super Efficient Power System complete with Solar Panels and Battery Back up System that Allows Highly Reduced Electic Bills!!! Whole House Water Filtration and Softening System, Custom Exterior Lighting Package, and Spacious Side-Entry Garage. Situated in the desirable community of The Overlook at Camp Creek, this residence combines style, comfort, and a prime location for the ultimate living experience.
